<title type="html"><![CDATA[8/29 (Thu.) 12 ways to reduce your cancer risk/10 Benefits of a Good Night's Sleep(Host:Cammy)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=311&amp;p=327#p327"><![CDATA[
Session I : 12 ways to reduce your cancer risk<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.cancer.ie/reduce-your-risk/healthy-lifestyle/europeancode#sthash.zaoS64vR.8rPYDnvr.dpbs">https://www.cancer.ie/reduce-your-risk/ ... YDnvr.dpbs</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion:<br />Q1: Do you hear any powerful survivor stories of cancer patients? Please share these stories about how their lives have been changed by cancer with your team members.<br /><br />Q2: This article provides 12 ways to reduce your cancer risk. Which ways do you want to try? Why?<br /><br />Q3: In this article mentioned that reduce the risk of cancer by ensuring your children take part in vaccination programs for Human Papillomavirus (HPV vaccine) (targeted for girls in first year of secondary school and upwards). Why do you agree your children to take HPV vaccine in school? Why not?<br /><br />Q4: How do you change your lifestyle and become a healthy person? Please share your comments at your table.<br /><br /><br />Session II : 10 Benefits of a Good Night's Sleep<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.verywellhealth.com/top-health-benefits-of-a-good-nights-sleep-2223766">https://www.verywellhealth.com/top-heal ... ep-2223766</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><br />Q1: How many hours do you need night’s sleep? Having trouble sleeping? Please share your experience with team members.<br /><br />Q2: How long can you go without sleep? What are the effect of lack sleep?<br /><br />Q3: Do you have some tips to help you overcome insomnia? Please share your experiences or your learning at your table.<br /><br />Q4: This article provides 10 benefits of good night’s sleep. Which points do you agree or disagree? Why?<br /><br />Suggested Agenda<br />7:00 p.m. --7:30 p.m. Free talk <br />7:30 p.m. --8:10 p.m. First topic discussion <br />8:10 p.m. --8:40 p.m. Presentation <br />8:40 p.m.-- 9.:15 p.m. Second topic discussion <br />9:15 p.m.-- 9:30 p.m. Presentation<br /><br />speaker time : 2 minutes for each speaker<br />host time : 3 minutes<br /><br />The meeting place of Thursday:<br />丹堤咖啡寶慶店：台北市延平南路107號2F (上樓右邊第三區塊)<br />捷運資訊： 近台北捷運–西門站 (4號出口步行約2分鐘，康是美隔壁)<br />丹堤低消: NT$80元<br />最自由的全英文會話聚會,前三次不用交會費,加入會員終生會費NT$500，帶著開放與熱情來學英文<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=13721">morris</a> — Fri Aug 23, 2019 2:24 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
